1. Danas se dogodio *sudar* dva automobila na raskrsnici. (Today there was a *collision* of two cars at the intersection.)
2. Vozači su izbegli *sudar* zahvaljujući brzom reagovanju. (The drivers avoided a *crash* thanks to their quick reactions.)
3. Nakon *sudara*, policija je blokirala ulicu da bi se uklonila oštećena vozila. (After the *collision*, the police blocked the street to remove the damaged vehicles.)
4. Vozila su se kretala u suprotnim smerovima, što je dovelo do *sudara*. (The vehicles were moving in opposite directions, which resulted in a *crash*.)
5. Putnici u autobusu su se uplašili kad su čuli zvuk *sudara* sa drugim vozilom. (The bus passengers were scared when they heard the sound of a *collision* with another vehicle.)
6. Ovaj automobil je pretrpeo velika oštećenja nakon *sudara* sa kamionom. (This car sustained heavy damage after a *crash* with a truck.)
7. Učesnici *sudara* su se žalili na bolove nakon nesreće. (The participants in the *collision* complained of pain after the accident.)
8. Sudije su doneli odluku u korist vozača koji nije bio kriv za *sudar*. (The judges ruled in favor of the driver who was not at fault for the *crash*.)
9. Vozači su se sukobili nakon *sudara* i morala je intervenisati policija. (The drivers got into a fight after the *collision* and the police had to intervene.)
10. *Sudar* je uzrokovao veliku gužvu u saobraćaju. (The *crash* caused a big traffic jam.)